        "authorId" : "b15d5707-82a8-4448-b49d-a2d6502b10f9",
        "body" : "I spent some time a few months ago trying to do an http2 implementation of the httpstream interfaces. I'm not sure it's going to be possible, or at least it won't be really easy. It's been a few months since I wrote this PR, so I don't remember the exact reason why I switched from io.Reader/Writer to httpstream.Stream. I'd have to go back and look.\n",
