        "authorId" : "b15d5707-82a8-4448-b49d-a2d6502b10f9",
        "body" : "Ok I remember why the v1 protocol has these as `httpstream.Stream` and not `io.Reader` etc - it's because the v1 protocol calls `Reset` on the streams. I'm updating v3 to use an `io.Writer` for `resizeStream`.\n",
